flowchart TD

%% Pipeline: Operational AI as a decision system (not a model race)

  

A[Operational reality<br/> sites, languages, exceptions] --> B[Data inputs]

B --> G1{Gate A<br/>Data readiness}

G1 -->|Pass| C[Model<br/>LLM / ML]

G1 -->|Fail| F1[Failure: Fragmented, inconsistent, unmonitored data<br/>Pilot works once, collapses at scale]

  

C --> D[Output<br/>recommendation / alert / forecast]

D --> G2{Gate B<br/>Decision ownership}

G2 -->|Pass| E[Decision & action<br/>embedded in workflow]

G2 -->|Fail| F2[Failure: Output has no owner<br/>Ignored dashboard or blame generator]

  

E --> G3{Gate C<br/>Oversight under pressure}

G3 -->|Pass| G4{Gate D<br/>Incentives & KPI guardrails}

G3 -->|Fail| F3[Failure: Over-reliance under pressure<br/>Humans stop challenging the system]

  

G4 -->|Pass| H[Production operations]

G4 -->|Fail| F4[Failure: Metric becomes the target<br/>Gaming, distorted signals, amplified bad behavior]

  

H --> G5{Gate E<br/>Operational control}

G5 -->|Pass| I[Governance & compliance<br/>envelope]

G5 -->|Fail| F5[Failure: Pilot cannot survive production<br/>No monitoring, change control, incidents, rollback]

  

I --> G6{Gate F<br/>Governance early}

G6 -->|Pass| J[Sustained adoption]

G6 -->|Fail| F6[Failure: Governance arrives late<br/>Blocked late or slowed until bypassed]

  

J --> G7{Gate G<br/>Operational pull}

G7 -->|Pass| K[Outcomes at scale<br/>AI as managed capability]

G7 -->|Fail| F7[Failure: Novelty-driven use case<br/>No enduring pain, no routines, adoption fades]

  

%% Callouts: the punchline

N1[Model quality reduces friction] -.-> C

N2[Operating model determines survival] -.-> G2

N2 -.-> G5

  

%% Minimal styling

classDef gate fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#c2410c,stroke-width:1px,color:#7c2d12;

classDef fail fill:#fef2f2,stroke:#b91c1c,stroke-width:1px,color:#7f1d1d;

classDef note fill:#eff6ff,stroke:#1d4ed8,stroke-width:1px,color:#1e3a8a;

  

class G1,G2,G3,G4,G5,G6,G7 gate;

class F1,F2,F3,F4,F5,F6,F7 fail;

class N1,N2 note;